    07_i386_exec_name (can be reintroduced in debian/rules)
    50_linuxbios_isa_bios_ram (shouldn't be needed anymore)
    51_linuxbios_piix_ram_size (applied)
    56_dhcp (crap)
    60_ppc_ld (reintroduce if needed)
    64_ppc_asm_constraints (ditto)
